      <body>
         <div xml:id="main">
            <head type="incipit">
               <supplied reason="XTF-compatibility">26/9/87 ¶  ¶ Allow me, dear Mr Maiden, to send the monthly remittance for Mr Baeuerlen again to you. If he does not collect much for technologic purposes early in the tour, he can — of course — do so ...</supplied>
            </head>
            <p rend="number" xml:lang="en">87.09.26</p>
            <p rend="correspondent" xml:lang="en">To Joseph Maiden</p>
            <p rend="location" xml:lang="en">MRS 202/97/<seg style="background-color: #ffff00; ">303 </seg>
               <seg style="font-weight: bold; background-color: #ffff00; ">[…]</seg>
               <seg style="background-color: #ffff00; ">,</seg> Powerhouse Museum, Sydney.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <note xml:id="ftn1" type="footnote" n="1">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <seg style="font-weight: bold; ">To proof.</seg>
                  </p>
               </note>
               <note xml:id="ftn2" type="footnote" n="2">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">MS is stamped and annotated: '<seg>THE TECHNOLOGICAL MUSEUM SYDNEY No. </seg>303<seg> RECEIVED SEP 28 1887</seg> Ansd. 28/9' and '<seg>SUBMITTED OCT 5 1887 TO THE TRUSTEES</seg>'. </p>
               </note>26/9/87</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Allow me, dear Mr Maiden, to send the monthly remittance for Mr Baeuerlen again to you. If he does not collect much for technologic purposes early in the tour, he can — of course — do so to the <seg style="">
                  <hi rend="underline">greatest</hi>
               </seg>
               <seg style="">
                  <hi rend="underline">advantage</hi>
               </seg> on his home-way, when he will know all the best "ins and outs".<note xml:id="ftn3" type="footnote" n="3">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">See J. Maiden to M, 12 September 1887.</p>
               </note>
            </p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Who should be most particularly honored with new plants of his being named?</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <seg style="">
                  <hi rend="underline">Do</hi>
               </seg> write to the Magistrate of the Hastings-Region, what <seg style="">
                  <hi rend="underline">really</hi>
               </seg> would be the means to get up to Mt Seaview;<note xml:id="ftn4" type="footnote" n="4">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">NSW; see M to Linnean Society of New South Wales, March 1887 (in this edition as 87-03-00c).</p>
               </note> I believe the difficulties to get there, have been greatly exaggerated. The police-officers of the District could give the clearest information on the subject.</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="en">Regardfully</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>your</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Ferd. von Mueller.</p>
         </div>
